summary: This script installs various text-based web browsers including lynx, links, w3m, elinks, and links2 using apt-get.

details.comment: This script installs various text-based web browsers including lynx, links, w3m, elinks, and links2 using apt-get.
details.content:
#!/bin/bash
apt-get install lynx
apt-get install links
apt-get install w3m
apt-get install elinks
apt-get install links2
